fn.p:
Manuscript has been revised in response to Review Commons Reviewer's comments. The main revisions are the following:
Figure 1 - panel A size was modified and new data were added to panel G;
Figure 2 - Additional panels showing systolic intervals (I) and diastolic diameters (L) are shown;
Figure S2 - additional control condition is provided (panel C)
Figure 3 - additional control condition (C57>LacZ) is provided (panels C, G, K, 0);
Figure 5 - New data are reported in panels G and H
Fig. S5 - Panel B has been modified
